        "subject": "LU-10073 tests: re-enable lnet selftest smoke test for PPC + ARM",
        "message": "LU-10073 tests: re-enable lnet selftest smoke test for PPC + ARM\n\nLNet selftest has failed on platforms with 64K pages. Recent work\nby Alexy Lyashkov should have resolved these issues. Lets enable\nthe lnet selftest to valid these changes.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial clientarch=aarch64 testlist=lnet-selftest\nTest-Parameters: trivial clientarch=ppc64 testlist=lnet-selftest\n\nChange-Id: Ia8b2b57f5401c9dafddb9d6b820560463dfcf415\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\n"
